2021年7月，EA宣布将推出《死亡空间》的重制版，将由{{le|EA Motive|Motive Studios}}负责开发，将使用EA的[[寒霜引擎|寒霜引擎]]重新制作；游戏将登陆[[Xbox_Series_X/S|Xbox Series X/S]]、[[PlayStation_5|PlayStation 5]]和Windows等平台。<ref>[https://www.gamespot.com/articles/dead-space-remake-announced-developed-by-ea-motive/1100-6494273/ Dead Space Remake Announced, Developed By EA Motive] {{Wayback|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/dead-space-remake-announced-developed-by-ea-motive/1100-6494273/ |date=20210722180149 }}.GameSpot.2021-07-22.[2021-07-23].</ref>

